Usage: set_net_group [-help] -reset | {-name <string> -type <string> -nets <string> }

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-name <string>                  # <net group name>> (string, required)
-nets <string>                  # <net names> (string, required)
-reset                          # <reset all previous set_net_group commands>
                                # (bool, optional)
-type <string>                  # <net group type> (string, required)